{"tid":2419643,"cid":25,"subCid":0,"title":"而加講買寵物要俾人起底","createTime":"2021-02-23T11:49:47.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-26T06:51:36.000Z","uid":133936,"like":11,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"7103b1f26c500e476336905a408ac1dced1649de","tid":2419643,"uid":133936,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-23T11:49:47.000Z","msg":"事源<br />\n<br />\n香港兔兔部落格 有人開post 講買兔仔<br />\nadmin即刻屌曬鬼 都明嘅 總有人接受唔到<br />\n但都唔洗起谷友底掛 人地仔女都起埋真心好痴線<br />\n跟住仲要覺得自己好撚好人<br />\n<br />\n話咩 唔中意咪去第二度囉 我起你底已經好少事<br />\n如果你出去出面後果更嚴重<br />\n<br />\n心諗再嚴重啲係咪約出嚟隻揪<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n唔知係咪心虛啦 del曬所有相關post and comment <br />\n平時最憎做正義撚 但今次忍唔撚到<br />\n順便俾大家見識下你隻藍絲八婆格啦<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/1mMw0qS.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F1mMw0qS.png&h=7a72f3c1&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/7FTrPjd.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F7FTrPjd.png&h=469bb5b6&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ORDO2Ee.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FORDO2Ee.png&h=4005a6cf&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n順便問下有冇黃嘅兔仔谷<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aa3abf12a38657b142bb25b451e45e3e1efd3802","tid":2419643,"uid":94958,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-23T11:50:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />道德撚"},{"pid":"72366b90c3f51a33326c36d302a3a8eca852d077","tid":2419643,"uid":133936,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"aa3abf12a38657b142bb25b451e45e3e1efd3802","tid":2419643,"uid":94958,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-23T11:50:46.000